game.name: Ellie Vogue Blog
game.description:
Ellie has a dynamic fashion sense and she also loves writing and posting articles on her personal fashion blog. Her excellent writing skills have allowed her to work as the editor of this popular Vogue blog. But, the problem is that she needs your help in taking some cool pictures and posting them on their blogs. Hey! Your good performance could also help the lady to bring some good money to her home. Would you like to accept this challenge? Join Ellie Vogue Blog and be prepared to run her personal blog successfully!

The best part is that you would find different types of outfits and other needful articles near to her in this brand new girlg game. So, all you need to go through them, prepare an awesome look, take pictures and upload them on the internet. Your job does not end her, but you also have to collect money for her and check if a blog you have worked for is profitable for her or not. Check out the wider and exclusive outfit collection and help the fashionista to create some cool and amazing outfits and post her look on her blog!

There are different fun summery crop tops to choose from. Give your model a lovely color top and match it with a fine skirt! Do not forget to accessorize your girl with a fabulous pair of chic sandals and a cute handbag. Pick the photo of that look and post the photo on the blog and then you would come forward to help Ellie to promote it and grab some cash earned from it. In the next article, you have to help a bride to select an awesome gown and combine it with shoes, veil and suitable hairstyle. Decorate an entire room in the third and last article in this cool dress-up game! Good luck to guide her to be the biggest vogue blogger!
